  {
    "i": 17,
    "alt": "🎅 PR Santa Smash Giveaway!\nPlay this December and stand a chance to win a premium Babolat racket from our Pro Shop (excl. LeBron models) 🎁🔥\n\nHere’s how it works ⬇️\n🎟 Earn tickets just by playing:\n• Weekend court bookings = 1 ticket per player (2-hour session, max 6 tickets)\n• Coaching sessions = 1 extra ticket per player\nNo limits — the more you play, the more chances you get!\n\nEligible formats: Private, Semi-Private, Group of 3, Play With The Coach\nFull-paying weekend bookings only.\n\n🎥 Live Draw\nHappening after the event. Draw will be recorded & shared.\n\n📅 Event Period: Weekends, 29 Nov – 28 Dec 2025\nPlay more, collect more, win big.\nLet’s close the year with a smash! 🎄🎾\n\n#PadelRevolution #PRSantasSmash #PadelMalaysia",
